               stealing, on the <rs id="t18280221-54-cd286" type="crimeDate">16th of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280221-54-off285 t18280221-54-cd286"></join>, 10 printed bound books, value 10s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               <persName id="t18280221-54-victim450" type="victimName">
                  Theodosius 
                  Williams
               <interp inst="t18280221-54-victim450" type="surname" value="Williams"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18280221-54-victim450" type="given" value="Theodosius"></interp>
